240
00:20:33,440 --> 00:20:34,440
"Saya suka awak, Shone."

241
00:20:35,600 --> 00:20:37,040
Daripada Crazy Little Thing Called Love.

242
00:20:37,080 --> 00:20:38,799
Sangat mengagumkan!

243
00:20:38,800 --> 00:20:42,280
Wah! Dia hampir memetik keseluruhan filem.

244
00:20:44,640 --> 00:20:46,680
Dia memetik setiap perkataan. Itu menakjubkan.

245
00:20:48,040 --> 00:20:49,200
Bagaimana anda ingat semua itu?

246
00:20:49,400 --> 00:20:51,600
Saya menggunakan monolog itu
